      "title": "Fort and Maradana railway stations staff away",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the people have been greatly inconvenienced by the withdrawal of staff at Colombo Fort and Maradana railway stations.",
        "Staff at Colombo Fort and Maradana railway stations have walked out as railway station workers started a strike to stop the entry and exit of trains demanding fuel, disrupting train operations."
